        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent. | Railway Station | Orpington. S.E.R.</hi></placeName>
                    <salute>My dear Galton</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>If you happen to be here about 5 will you pay us a visit, as I hope by that time to be rested &amp; alive</p>
<p>Yours very sincerely | Ch. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

            
            
            
            
            
            
